OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780589464
OL,3,CStonehenge mystery: Altar stone moved
OL,4,Cby glacier and ancient rescue mission
OL,6,FThe altar stone of Stonehenge could
OL,7,Fhave travelled from north-east
OL,8,FScotland via glacier before reaching
OL,9,FSalisbury Plain, a study has found.
OL,11,FThe six-tonne, sandstone monolith is
OL,12,Fbelieved to have originated in the
OL,13,FOrcadian Basin in northern Scotland `
OL,14,Fbut the mystery of how it reached
OL,15,FSalisbury Plain, about 435 miles away,
OL,16,Fhas remained unsolved.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
