PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780589464
OL,3,CStonehenge mystery: Altar stone moved
OL,4,Cby glacier and ancient rescue mission
OL,6,FNow researchers at Sheffield Hallam
OL,7,FUniversity and Curtin University in
OL,8,FAustralia have found the stone may
OL,9,Fhave travelled via glacier to
OL,10,FDoggerland, a neolithic site off the
OL,11,Feast coast of England, during the last
OL,12,FIce Age.
OL,14,FAfter being deposited by the glacier
OL,15,Fin Doggerland, prehistoric Britons may
OL,16,Fhave transported the block south to
OL,17,Fits final resting place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/11
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
