PN,41511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1780589464
OL,3,CStonehenge mystery: Altar stone moved
OL,4,Cby glacier and ancient rescue mission
OL,6,FFuture research will aim to pinpoint
OL,7,Fthe altar stone's exact source in
OL,8,Fnorth-east Scotland and further
OL,9,Finvestigate possible transport routes
OL,10,Fused by prehistoric communities.
OL,12,FThe study, From Highlands To Henge:
OL,13,FRefining The Provenance And Transport
OL,14,FPathways Of Stonehenge's Altar Stone,
OL,15,Fwas published in the Journal of
OL,16,FQuaternary Science.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/11
